

{{#partial "content"}}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Wildlife-Tracker</title>
<!--    <link rel='stylesheet' href='https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.2.0/css/bootstrap.min.css'>-->

    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/css/app.css'>
    <script src='js/jquery-3.5.1.js'></script>
       <script src="/js/app.js"></script>
</head>
<body style="background-color: burlywood">
    <h1 class="h1 text-center text-danger"> Chui Wildlife Trackers</h1>

    <div class="what-we-do mt-5">

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div id="design">
                    <h2 class="title">Endangered Animals</h2>
                    <p>Earth is blessed with a stunning variety of wildlife – it has more species of charismatic megafauna than any other continent. However, sadly, with ever expanding human populations and their increasing demand for land, food and water, exacerbated by poaching, more and more species are becoming endangered. However, thanks to the foresight of conservationists past and present, many of the most endangered animals  are being protected in reserves and national parks.</p>
                    <p>Endangered species may be at risk due to factors such as habitat loss, poaching and invasive species.Here at Chui Wildlife trackers we rescue and protect most of this animals</p>
                </div>
                <div id="designImage">
                    <img src="/images/unnamed.jpg" height="200cm" width="300cm"  alt="design">
                    <p>Endangered Animals</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div id="development">
                    <h2 class="title">About Us</h2>
                    <p>Chui Wildlife Tracking is a an animal reserve whose main purpose is to cater for the needs of wildlife
                    </p>
                    <p>We rescue vulnerable and endangered animals</p>
                </div>
                <div id="developmentImage">
                    <img src="/images/about.jpg" height="200cm" width="300cm" alt="development">
                    <P>About us</P>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div id="product">
                    <h2 class="title">Adopt An Animal</h2>
                    <p id> Chui Wildlife Adoption program lets you symbolically adopt your favorite species and at the same time support our important work that is , taking care of the animals</p>
                    <p>Offer Life and Hope to an Animal in Need by Adopting an Orphan Elephant or Rhino. Adopt an Endangered Animal for Yourself or as a Gift from $50 / £35 a Year.</p>
                </div>
                <div id="productImage">
                    <img src="/images/adopt.jpg" height="200cm" width="300cm"  alt="products">
                    <P>Adopt An Animal</P>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card bg-white mt-5 text-white">
<!--        <img src="/images/images.jpeg" class="card-img" alt="contact background">-->
        <div class="card-img-overlay">
            <h2 class="contact text-center text-dark">CONTACT US</h2>
            <form>
                <div class="form-row">
                    <div class="col">
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="name" placeholder="Name" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col">
                        <input type="email" class="form-control" id="email" placeholder="Email" required>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <textarea class="form-control" rows="8" id="comment" placeholder="Your message here...."></textarea>
                </div>
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary col-md-1">Submit</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="/js/app.js"></script>
</body>
<html>
